# Photo Eye Parameters
````ad-note
title: Template
collapse: open
#### Photo Eye Floor Number
Name: 

Item | Parameters
-|-
BF_#: | BF_#
Alias: | I_#.#
Point Alias: | \<A30501_DIN_AI:I:Data[#].#>
Dark (0) or Light (1) | #

```ad-tip

Alias should always be one "one's" place lower than the Point I/O location
example:
I_***26.1*** <-> \<A30501_DIN_AI:I:Data***[27].1***>

When trying to find the wires associated with the Point I/O block use the Bolded number below to find:

\<**A30501**_DIN_AI:I:Data**[27].1**>

This will be Point I/O chasis **A30501** -> Card **27** -> terminal **1**

**Note**: *This is not applicable to the box conveyors*
````

NU = Not Used
